\v 23 if indeed you continue¦132957 on in your established¦132960 and firm faith¦132959. Don't let \add anyone\add* drive away the hope that \add comes from\add* the good message that you all heard¦132973 and which has been proclaimed¦132975 throughout the whole world—it's that good message that I've become a servant¦132992 of.
\s1 Paul's work for believers
\rem /s1 Paul's Work as a Servant of the Church; Paul's Interest in the Colossians; Paul's Labour for the Church; Paul's Work for the Church
\p
\v 24 So now I'm happy to be suffering¦132998 for you all, and I'm catching up in my¦133014 body to the tribulations¦133008 of the \nd messiah¦133010\nd* in his¦133018 body, which¦133019 is the assembly¦133023.
