\v 19 \x + \xo 2:19: \xt Eph 4:16.\x*They're not listening to the head which controls all the joints¦133491 and ligaments¦133493 of the body¦133487 and holds it all together¦133496 as \nd God¦133502\nd* causes it to grow.
