\v 5 So¦133621 put your¦133622 earthly¦133628 natures to death: sexual¦133629 immorality¦133629, impurity¦133630, passion¦133631, evil¦133633 desires¦133632, and¦133634 greediness¦133636 which is idolatry¦133639,
