\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 4:1: \xt Eph 6:9.\x*\nd You\nd* masters, ensure that you're treating your slaves¦133993 with goodness and equality¦133991, knowing¦133996 that you all also have a master \add of your own\add* in heaven¦134004.
