\p
\v 7 \x + \xo 4:7: \xt Acts 20:4; 2Tim 4:12.\x*My dear brother¦134084 and faithful¦134086 servant¦134087 and fellow¦134089 slave, Tychicus, will tell you¦134080 all about me.
